<lb n="0508b14" ed="T"/>
<lb n="0508b15" ed="T"/><head type="no">No. 118 [No. 99(1077), No. 100(16), No.
<lb n="0508b16" ed="T"/>125(38.6), Nos. 119-120]</head><div1 type="jing">
<lb n="0508b17" ed="T"/><juan n="001" fun="open"><mulu n="001" type="卷"/><jhead><title>佛說<note n="0508003" resp="Taisho" place="foot text" type="orig">鴦掘摩＝鴦崛摩【三】</note><note n="0508003" resp="CBETA" type="mod">鴦掘摩＝鴦崛摩【宋】【元】【明】</note><app n="0508003"><lem wit="【大】">鴦掘摩</lem><rdg resp="Taisho" wit="【宋】【元】【明】">鴦崛摩</rdg></app>經</title></jhead></juan>
<lb n="0508b18" ed="T"/>
<lb n="0508b19" ed="T"/><byline type="Translator">西晉<note n="0508004" resp="Taisho" place="foot text" type="orig">〔月氏國〕－【三】</note><note n="0508004" resp="CBETA" type="mod">〔月氏國〕－【宋】【元】【明】</note><app n="0508004"><lem wit="【大】">月氏國</lem><rdg resp="Taisho" wit="【宋】【元】【明】">&lac;</rdg></app><note n="0508005" resp="Taisho" place="foot text" type="orig">三藏＋（法師）【三】</note><note n="0508005" resp="CBETA" type="mod">三藏＋（法師）【宋】【元】【明】</note><app n="0508005"><lem wit="【大】">三藏</lem><rdg resp="Taisho" wit="【宋】【元】【明】">三藏法師</rdg></app>竺法護譯</byline>
<lb n="0508b20" ed="T"/><p id="pT02p0508b2001">聞如是。一時佛遊舍衛國祇樹給孤獨園。與
<lb n="0508b21" ed="T"/>大比丘五百眾俱。舍衛城中有異梵志。博綜
<lb n="0508b22" ed="T"/>三經無所疑滯。具暢五典所問即對。精生講
<lb n="0508b23" ed="T"/>肆莫不稟仰。國老諮<note n="0508006" resp="Taisho" place="foot text" type="orig">諏＝趣【三】</note><note n="0508006" resp="CBETA" type="mod">諏＝趣【宋】【元】【明】</note><app n="0508006"><lem wit="【大】">諏</lem><rdg resp="Taisho" wit="【宋】【元】【明】">趣</rdg></app>群儒宗焉。門徒濟濟
<lb n="0508b24" ed="T"/>有五百人。上首弟子名<note n="0508007" resp="Taisho" place="foot text" type="orig">鴦掘摩＝鴦崛摩【明】＊</note><app n="0508007"><lem wit="【大】">鴦掘摩</lem><rdg resp="Taisho" wit="【明】">鴦崛摩</rdg></app><note n="0508008" resp="Taisho" place="foot text" type="orig">〔晉曰指鬘〕－【明】</note><app n="0508008"><lem wit="【大】"><note place="inline">晉曰指鬘</note></lem><rdg resp="Taisho" wit="【明】">&lac;</rdg></app>。儀幹剛
<lb n="0508b25" ed="T"/>猛力超壯士。手能接飛走先奔馬。聰慧才辯
<lb n="0508b26" ed="T"/>志性和雅。安詳敏達一無疑礙。色像第一師
<lb n="0508b27" ed="T"/>所嘉異。<note n="0508009" resp="Taisho" place="foot text" type="orig">室主＝室生【三】</note><note n="0508009" resp="CBETA" type="mod">室主＝室生【宋】【元】【明】</note><app n="0508009"><lem wit="【大】">室主</lem><rdg resp="Taisho" wit="【宋】【元】【明】">室生</rdg></app>欽敬候夫出處。往造指鬘而謂
<lb n="0508b28" ed="T"/>之曰。觀爾顏彩有堂堂之容。推步年齒相覺
<lb n="0508b29" ed="T"/>不殊。寧可同歡接所娛乎。指鬘聞之慞惶怖
<pb n="0508c" id="T02.0118.0508c" ed="T"/>
<lb n="0508c01" ed="T"/>懼。毛衣起&CB00594;跪而答曰。夫人比母師則當父。
<lb n="0508c02" ed="T"/>猥垂斯教<note n="0508010" resp="Taisho" place="foot text" type="orig">儀＝義【三】</note><note n="0508010" resp="CBETA" type="mod">儀＝義【宋】【元】【明】</note><app n="0508010"><lem wit="【大】">儀</lem><rdg resp="Taisho" wit="【宋】【元】【明】">義</rdg></app>不敢許。心所不甘甚非法也。師
<lb n="0508c03" ed="T"/>婦又曰。飢者與食渴給水漿有何非法。寒施
<lb n="0508c04" ed="T"/>溫衣熱惠清涼有何非法。裸露復之危厄救
<lb n="0508c05" ed="T"/>之有何非法。指鬘答曰。赴趣患急<note n="0508011" resp="Taisho" place="foot text" type="orig">寬＝救【三】</note><note n="0508011" resp="CBETA" type="mod">寬＝救【宋】【元】【明】</note><app n="0508011"><lem wit="【大】">寬</lem><rdg resp="Taisho" wit="【宋】【元】【明】">救</rdg></app>濟窮
<lb n="0508c06" ed="T"/>頓實無非法。夫人母也。師之所重。隨婬著色
<lb n="0508c07" ed="T"/>慢犯非宜。如蛇<note n="0508012" resp="Taisho" place="foot text" type="orig">蝘＝繳【宋】，&CB04825;【元】【明】</note><note n="0508012" resp="CBETA" type="mod">蝘＝繳【宋】，＝&CB04825;【元】【明】</note><app n="0508012"><lem wit="【大】">蝘</lem><rdg resp="Taisho" wit="【宋】">繳</rdg><rdg resp="Taisho" wit="【元】【明】">&CB04825;</rdg></app>體服毒<note n="0508013" resp="Taisho" place="foot text" type="orig">褒＝喪身【三】</note><note n="0508013" resp="CBETA" type="mod">褒＝喪身【宋】【元】【明】</note><app n="0508013"><lem wit="【大】">褒</lem><rdg resp="Taisho" wit="【宋】【元】【明】">喪身</rdg></app>。師室聞之即
<lb n="0508c08" ed="T"/>懷<note n="0508014" resp="Taisho" place="foot text" type="orig">愧＝媿【三】</note><note n="0508014" resp="CBETA" type="mod">愧＝媿【宋】【元】【明】</note><app n="0508014"><lem wit="【大】">愧</lem><rdg resp="Taisho" wit="【宋】【元】【明】">媿</rdg></app>恨。歸自總<note n="0508015" resp="Taisho" place="foot text" type="orig">滅＝搣摧【三】</note><note n="0508015" resp="CBETA" type="mod">滅＝搣摧【宋】【元】【明】</note><app n="0508015"><lem wit="【大】">滅</lem><rdg resp="Taisho" wit="【宋】【元】【明】">搣摧</rdg></app>裂衣裳。&CB00614;金黃面佯愁
<lb n="0508c09" ed="T"/>委臥。時夫行還。問曰。何故有何不善。誰相
<lb n="0508c10" ed="T"/><note n="0508016" resp="Taisho" place="foot text" type="orig">嬲＝嬈【三】</note><note n="0508016" resp="CBETA" type="mod">嬲＝嬈【宋】【元】【明】</note><app n="0508016"><lem wit="【大】">嬲</lem><rdg resp="Taisho" wit="【宋】【元】【明】">嬈</rdg></app>觸。室人譖曰。君常所歎聰慧弟子。柔仁
<lb n="0508c11" ed="T"/>貞潔履行無闕。君旦不在來<note n="0508017" resp="Taisho" place="foot text" type="orig">見＝相【三】</note><note n="0508017" resp="CBETA" type="mod">見＝相【宋】【元】【明】</note><app n="0508017"><lem wit="【大】">見</lem><rdg resp="Taisho" wit="【宋】【元】【明】">相</rdg></app>牽掣。欲肆
<lb n="0508c12" ed="T"/>逆慢妾不順從。而被<note n="0508018" resp="Taisho" place="foot text" type="orig">陵＝凌【三】</note><note n="0508018" resp="CBETA" type="mod">陵＝凌【宋】【元】【明】</note><app n="0508018"><lem wit="【大】">陵</lem><rdg resp="Taisho" wit="【宋】【元】【明】">凌</rdg></app>侮摧<note n="0508019" resp="Taisho" place="foot text" type="orig">捽＝碎【三】</note><note n="0508019" resp="CBETA" type="mod">捽＝碎【宋】【元】【明】</note><app n="0508019"><lem wit="【大】">捽</lem><rdg resp="Taisho" wit="【宋】【元】【明】">碎</rdg></app>委頓。是以
<lb n="0508c13" ed="T"/>受辱不能自起。師聞悵然意懷盛怒。欲加楚
<lb n="0508c14" ed="T"/>罰掠治姦暴。慮之雄霸非力所伏。退欲靜默
<lb n="0508c15" ed="T"/>深惟不道。穢染閨閤上下失<note n="0508020" resp="Taisho" place="foot text" type="orig">序＝緒【三】</note><note n="0508020" resp="CBETA" type="mod">序＝緒【宋】【元】【明】</note><app n="0508020"><lem wit="【大】">序</lem><rdg resp="Taisho" wit="【宋】【元】【明】">緒</rdg></app>。進退沈吟將
<lb n="0508c16" ed="T"/>如之何。乃<note n="0508021" resp="Taisho" place="foot text" type="orig">咿＝依【宋】，伊【元】【明】</note><note n="0508021" resp="CBETA" type="mod">咿＝依【宋】，＝伊【元】【明】</note><app n="0508021"><lem wit="【大】">咿</lem><rdg resp="Taisho" wit="【宋】">依</rdg><rdg resp="Taisho" wit="【元】【明】">伊</rdg></app>悒歎曰。當微改常倒教而教。
<lb n="0508c17" ed="T"/>教使殺人限至于百。各貫一指以鬘其額。殺
<lb n="0508c18" ed="T"/>人之罪罪莫大焉。不加楚酷必就辜戮。現受
<lb n="0508c19" ed="T"/>危沒<note n="0508022" resp="Taisho" place="foot text" type="orig">沒＝死【三】</note><note n="0508022" resp="CBETA" type="mod">沒＝死【宋】【元】【明】</note><app n="0508022"><lem wit="【大】">沒</lem><rdg resp="Taisho" wit="【宋】【元】【明】">死</rdg></app>墮地獄。不可釋<note n="0508023" resp="Taisho" place="foot text" type="orig">〔置〕－【三】</note><note n="0508023" resp="CBETA" type="mod">〔置〕－【宋】【元】【明】</note><app n="0508023"><lem wit="【大】">置</lem><rdg resp="Taisho" wit="【宋】【元】【明】">&lac;</rdg></app>縱使<note n="0508024" resp="Taisho" place="foot text" type="orig">滋＝茲【三】</note><note n="0508024" resp="CBETA" type="mod">滋＝茲【宋】【元】【明】</note><app n="0508024"><lem wit="【大】">滋</lem><rdg resp="Taisho" wit="【宋】【元】【明】">茲</rdg></app>甚也。</p>
<lb n="0508c20" ed="T"/><p id="pT02p0508c2001">於是師命指鬘而<note n="0508025" resp="Taisho" place="foot text" type="orig">告＋（之）【三】</note><note n="0508025" resp="CBETA" type="mod">告＋（之）【宋】【元】【明】</note><app n="0508025"><lem wit="【大】">告</lem><rdg resp="Taisho" wit="【宋】【元】【明】">告之</rdg></app>曰。卿之聰慧所學周密。
<lb n="0508c21" ed="T"/><note n="0508026" resp="Taisho" place="foot text" type="orig">升＝計昇【三】</note><note n="0508026" resp="CBETA" type="mod">升＝計昇【宋】【元】【明】</note><app n="0508026"><lem wit="【大】">升</lem><rdg resp="Taisho" wit="【宋】【元】【明】">計昇</rdg></app>堂入室精生無首。唯之一藝未施行耳。
<lb n="0508c22" ed="T"/>指鬘進曰。願聞所告。師曰。欲速成者宜執
<lb n="0508c23" ed="T"/>利劍。晨於四衢躬殺百人。人取一指以為傅
<lb n="0508c24" ed="T"/>飾。至于日中使百指滿。設勤奉遵。則道德
<lb n="0508c25" ed="T"/>備矣。便以&CB00669;授。指鬘受劍聞告愕懼。心懷
<lb n="0508c26" ed="T"/>愁慼。設違教旨非孝弟子。順而行之畏陷失
<lb n="0508c27" ed="T"/>理。奉劍而退垂淚言曰。淨修梵行則梵志法。
<lb n="0508c28" ed="T"/>孝養父母則梵志法。修為眾善則梵志法。不
<lb n="0508c29" ed="T"/><note n="0508027" resp="Taisho" place="foot text" type="orig">邪＝矯【三】</note><note n="0508027" resp="CBETA" type="mod">邪＝矯【宋】【元】【明】</note><app n="0508027"><lem wit="【大】">邪</lem><rdg resp="Taisho" wit="【宋】【元】【明】">矯</rdg></app>正歸則梵志法。柔和<note n="0508028" resp="Taisho" place="foot text" type="orig">仁惠＝仁慧【三】</note><note n="0508028" resp="CBETA" type="mod">仁惠＝仁慧【宋】【元】【明】</note><app n="0508028"><lem wit="【大】">仁惠</lem><rdg resp="Taisho" wit="【宋】【元】【明】">仁慧</rdg></app>則梵志法。弘
<pb n="0509a" id="T02.0118.0509a" ed="T"/>
<lb n="0509a01" ed="T"/>慈四等則梵志。法得五神通則梵志法。超上
<lb n="0509a02" ed="T"/>梵天則梵志法。今暴伐殺非法失理。躊躇懊
<lb n="0509a03" ed="T"/>惱當如之何。即詣<note n="0509001" resp="Taisho" place="foot text" type="orig">前＝叢【三】</note><note n="0509001" resp="CBETA" type="mod">前＝叢【宋】【元】【明】</note><app n="0509001"><lem wit="【大】">前</lem><rdg resp="Taisho" wit="【宋】【元】【明】">叢</rdg></app>樹四衢路側。悲怒<note n="0509002" resp="Taisho" place="foot text" type="orig">激＝憿【三】</note><note n="0509002" resp="CBETA" type="mod">激＝憿【宋】【元】【明】</note><app n="0509002"><lem wit="【大】">激</lem><rdg resp="Taisho" wit="【宋】【元】【明】">憿</rdg></app>
<lb n="0509a04" ed="T"/>憤惡鬼助禍。耗亂其心瞋目噴吒。四顧遠視
<lb n="0509a05" ed="T"/>如鬼師子。如虎<note n="0509003" resp="Taisho" place="foot text" type="orig">狼＝猛【三】</note><note n="0509003" resp="CBETA" type="mod">狼＝猛【宋】【元】【明】</note><app n="0509003"><lem wit="【大】">狼</lem><rdg resp="Taisho" wit="【宋】【元】【明】">猛</rdg></app>獸跳騰馳踊。色貌可畏
<lb n="0509a06" ed="T"/>行者四集。悉當趣城即奮長劍多所殺害。莫
<lb n="0509a07" ed="T"/>不迸怖值無遺脫。去來往返而無覺者。無數
<lb n="0509a08" ed="T"/>之眾稱怨悲叫。入<note n="0509004" resp="Taisho" place="foot text" type="orig">趣＝赴【三】</note><note n="0509004" resp="CBETA" type="mod">趣＝赴【宋】【元】【明】</note><app n="0509004"><lem wit="【大】">趣</lem><rdg resp="Taisho" wit="【宋】【元】【明】">赴</rdg></app>王宮告有逆賊。遮截要
<lb n="0509a09" ed="T"/>路害人不少。唯願<note n="0509005" resp="Taisho" place="foot text" type="orig">天王＝大王【三】</note><note n="0509005" resp="CBETA" type="mod">天王＝大王【宋】【元】【明】</note><app n="0509005"><lem wit="【大】">天王</lem><rdg resp="Taisho" wit="【宋】【元】【明】">大王</rdg></app>。為民除患。時諸比
<lb n="0509a10" ed="T"/>丘入城分衛見諸告者。恐怖如是。分衛還出
<lb n="0509a11" ed="T"/>飯食畢訖。往詣佛所稽首足下白世尊曰。見
<lb n="0509a12" ed="T"/>國人眾詣王宮門。<note n="0509006" resp="Taisho" place="foot text" type="orig">告＋（有）【三】</note><note n="0509006" resp="CBETA" type="mod">告＋（有）【宋】【元】【明】</note><app n="0509006"><lem wit="【大】">告</lem><rdg resp="Taisho" wit="【宋】【元】【明】">告有</rdg></app>大逆賊名曰指鬘。手執
<lb n="0509a13" ed="T"/>利劍多所危害。體掌污血路無行人。</p>
<lb n="0509a14" ed="T"/><p id="pT02p0509a1401">爾時世尊告諸比丘。汝等且止。吾往救之。佛
<lb n="0509a15" ed="T"/>從坐起尋到其所。道逢&CB00034;牧荷負載乘。佃居
<lb n="0509a16" ed="T"/><note n="0509007" resp="Taisho" place="foot text" type="orig">民眾＝眾民【三】</note><note n="0509007" resp="CBETA" type="mod">民眾＝眾民【宋】【元】【明】</note><app n="0509007"><lem wit="【大】">民眾</lem><rdg resp="Taisho" wit="【宋】【元】【明】">眾民</rdg></app>白世尊曰。大聖所湊<note n="0509008" resp="Taisho" place="foot text" type="orig">勿＝無【三】</note><note n="0509008" resp="CBETA" type="mod">勿＝無【宋】【元】【明】</note><app n="0509008"><lem wit="【大】">勿</lem><rdg resp="Taisho" wit="【宋】【元】【明】">無</rdg></app>由斯路。前有
<lb n="0509a17" ed="T"/>逆賊四徼道斷。<note n="0509009" resp="Taisho" place="foot text" type="orig">取＝所【三】</note><note n="0509009" resp="CBETA" type="mod">取＝所【宋】【元】【明】</note><app n="0509009"><lem wit="【大】">取</lem><rdg resp="Taisho" wit="【宋】【元】【明】">所</rdg></app>殺狼藉唯改所從。又且獨
<lb n="0509a18" ed="T"/>步<note n="0509010" resp="Taisho" place="foot text" type="orig">無＋（有）【三】</note><note n="0509010" resp="CBETA" type="mod">無＋（有）【宋】【元】【明】</note><app n="0509010"><lem wit="【大】">無</lem><rdg resp="Taisho" wit="【宋】【元】【明】">無有</rdg></app>侍衛故也。世尊告曰。設使三界盡為寇
<lb n="0509a19" ed="T"/>虜吾不省錄。況一賊乎。指鬘之母怪子不歸。
<lb n="0509a20" ed="T"/>時至不食懼必當飢。齎餉出城就<note n="0509011" resp="Taisho" place="foot text" type="orig">而＝如【三】</note><note n="0509011" resp="CBETA" type="mod">而＝如【宋】【元】【明】</note><app n="0509011"><lem wit="【大】">而</lem><rdg resp="Taisho" wit="【宋】【元】【明】">如</rdg></app>餉之日
<lb n="0509a21" ed="T"/><note n="0509012" resp="Taisho" place="foot text" type="orig">欲向＝向欲【三】</note><note n="0509012" resp="CBETA" type="mod">欲向＝向欲【宋】【元】【明】</note><app n="0509012"><lem wit="【大】">欲向</lem><rdg resp="Taisho" wit="【宋】【元】【明】">向欲</rdg></app>中百指未滿。恐日移昳道業不具。欲還
<lb n="0509a22" ed="T"/>害母以充其數。佛念指鬘若害母者。在不中
<lb n="0509a23" ed="T"/>止罪不可救。佛便忽然住立其前。時<app source="0508007" type="＊"><lem wit="【大】">鴦掘摩</lem><rdg resp="Taisho" wit="【明】">鴦崛摩</rdg></app>
<lb n="0509a24" ed="T"/>見佛捨母。如師子步往迎世尊。心自念言。十
<lb n="0509a25" ed="T"/>人百人見我馳迸<note n="0509013" resp="Taisho" place="foot text" type="orig">不＝莫【三】</note><note n="0509013" resp="CBETA" type="mod">不＝莫【宋】【元】【明】</note><app n="0509013"><lem wit="【大】">不</lem><rdg resp="Taisho" wit="【宋】【元】【明】">莫</rdg></app>敢當也。吾常奮威縱橫
<lb n="0509a26" ed="T"/>自恣。況此沙門獨身<note n="0509014" resp="Taisho" place="foot text" type="orig">而至＝如此【三】</note><note n="0509014" resp="CBETA" type="mod">而至＝如此【宋】【元】【明】</note><app n="0509014"><lem wit="【大】">而至</lem><rdg resp="Taisho" wit="【宋】【元】【明】">如此</rdg></app>。<note n="0509015" resp="Taisho" place="foot text" type="orig">今＝當【明】</note><app n="0509015"><lem wit="【大】">今</lem><rdg resp="Taisho" wit="【明】">當</rdg></app>我規圖必勦
<lb n="0509a27" ed="T"/>其命。<note n="0509016" resp="Taisho" place="foot text" type="orig">即＝便【三】</note><note n="0509016" resp="CBETA" type="mod">即＝便【宋】【元】【明】</note><app n="0509016"><lem wit="【大】">即</lem><rdg resp="Taisho" wit="【宋】【元】【明】">便</rdg></app>執劍趣佛不能自前竭力奔走亦不
<lb n="0509a28" ed="T"/>能到則心念曰。我跳度江河解諸繫縛。<note n="0509017" resp="Taisho" place="foot text" type="orig">投＝捉【三】</note><note n="0509017" resp="CBETA" type="mod">投＝捉【宋】【元】【明】</note><app n="0509017"><lem wit="【大】">投</lem><rdg resp="Taisho" wit="【宋】【元】【明】">捉</rdg></app>捭
<lb n="0509a29" ed="T"/>勇猛曾無匹敵。重關固塞無不開<note n="0509018" resp="Taisho" place="foot text" type="orig">闔＝闢【三】</note><note n="0509018" resp="CBETA" type="mod">闔＝闢【宋】【元】【明】</note><app n="0509018"><lem wit="【大】">闔</lem><rdg resp="Taisho" wit="【宋】【元】【明】">闢</rdg></app>。而此沙
<pb n="0509b" id="T02.0118.0509b" ed="T"/>
<lb n="0509b01" ed="T"/>門徐步<note n="0509019" resp="Taisho" place="foot text" type="orig">裁＝纔【三】</note><note n="0509019" resp="CBETA" type="mod">裁＝纔【宋】【元】【明】</note><app n="0509019"><lem wit="【大】">裁</lem><rdg resp="Taisho" wit="【宋】【元】【明】">纔</rdg></app>動我走不及。殫盡威勢永不摩近。
<lb n="0509b02" ed="T"/>指鬘謂佛。沙門且止。佛告逆賊。吾止<note n="0509020" resp="Taisho" place="foot text" type="orig">已＝以【三】＊</note><note n="0509020" resp="CBETA" type="mod">已＝以【宋】＊【元】＊【明】＊</note><app n="0509020"><lem wit="【大】">已</lem><rdg resp="Taisho" wit="【宋】【元】【明】">以</rdg></app>來
<lb n="0509b03" ed="T"/>其日久矣。但汝未止。時<app source="0508007" type="＊"><lem wit="【大】">鴦掘摩</lem><rdg resp="Taisho" wit="【明】">鴦崛摩</rdg></app>遙以偈頌曰。</p>
<lb n="0509b04" ed="T"/><lg id="lgT02p0509b0401"><l>寂志語何謂</l><l>自云已停跱</l>
<lb n="0509b05" ed="T"/><l>斯言何所趣</l><l>以我為不止</l>
<lb n="0509b06" ed="T"/><l>今佛云何立</l><l>謂身行不住</l>
<lb n="0509b07" ed="T"/><l>反以我若茲</l><l>願說解此義</l></lg>
<lb n="0509b08" ed="T"/><p id="pT02p0509b0801">於是世尊為指鬘頌偈。而告之曰。</p>
<lb n="0509b09" ed="T"/><lg id="lgT02p0509b0901"><l>指鬘聽佛住</l><l>世尊<note n="0509021" resp="Taisho" place="foot text" type="orig">除君過＝降群愚【三】</note><note n="0509021" resp="CBETA" type="mod">除君過＝降群愚【宋】【元】【明】</note><app n="0509021"><lem wit="【大】">除君過</lem><rdg resp="Taisho" wit="【宋】【元】【明】">降群愚</rdg></app></l>
<lb n="0509b10" ed="T"/><l>汝走無<note n="0509022" resp="Taisho" place="foot text" type="orig">智＝知【三】</note><note n="0509022" resp="CBETA" type="mod">智＝知【宋】【元】【明】</note><app n="0509022"><lem wit="【大】">智</lem><rdg resp="Taisho" wit="【宋】【元】【明】">知</rdg></app>想</l><l>吾定爾不止</l>
<lb n="0509b11" ed="T"/><l>吾安住三脫</l><l>樂法修梵行</l>
<lb n="0509b12" ed="T"/><l>汝獨驅<note n="0509023" resp="Taisho" place="foot text" type="orig">癡＝疑【三】</note><note n="0509023" resp="CBETA" type="mod">癡＝疑【宋】【元】【明】</note><app n="0509023"><lem wit="【大】">癡</lem><rdg resp="Taisho" wit="【宋】【元】【明】">疑</rdg></app>想</l><l>懷害今<note n="0509024" resp="Taisho" place="foot text" type="orig">未＝不【三】</note><note n="0509024" resp="CBETA" type="mod">未＝不【宋】【元】【明】</note><app n="0509024"><lem wit="【大】">未</lem><rdg resp="Taisho" wit="【宋】【元】【明】">不</rdg></app>止</l>
<lb n="0509b13" ed="T"/><l>大聖無極慧</l><l><note n="0509025" resp="Taisho" place="foot text" type="orig">讚＝講【三】</note><note n="0509025" resp="CBETA" type="mod">讚＝講【宋】【元】【明】</note><app n="0509025"><lem wit="【大】">讚</lem><rdg resp="Taisho" wit="【宋】【元】【明】">講</rdg></app>寂於四衢</l>
<lb n="0509b14" ed="T"/><l>尋聞所說罪</l><l>聽<note n="0509026" resp="Taisho" place="foot text" type="orig">釆詠＝採訓【三】</note><note n="0509026" resp="CBETA" type="mod"><app><lem resp="CBETA.say">采</lem><rdg wit="【大】">釆</rdg></app>詠＝採訓【宋】【元】【明】<app><lem resp="CBETA.say" cf1="K19p599b03">，＝釆詠【麗】</lem><rdg wit="【大】"></rdg></app></note><app n="0509026"><lem wit="【大】">采詠</lem><rdg resp="Taisho" wit="【宋】【元】【明】">採訓</rdg><rdg resp="CBETA.say" cf1="K19p599b03" wit="【麗】">釆詠</rdg></app>法義</l></lg>
<lb n="0509b15" ed="T"/><p id="pT02p0509b1501">於是指鬘心<note n="0509027" resp="Taisho" place="foot text" type="orig">即＝自【明】</note><app n="0509027"><lem wit="【大】">即</lem><rdg resp="Taisho" wit="【明】">自</rdg></app>開悟。棄劍稽首自投于地。唯
<lb n="0509b16" ed="T"/>願世尊。恕我迷謬。興害集指念欲見道。僥賴
<lb n="0509b17" ed="T"/>慈化乞原罪舋。垂哀接濟得使出家受成就
<lb n="0509b18" ed="T"/>戒。佛則授之即為沙門。</p>
<lb n="0509b19" ed="T"/><p id="pT02p0509b1901">爾時世尊威神巍巍。智慧<note n="0509028" resp="Taisho" place="foot text" type="orig">光明＝光光【三】</note><note n="0509028" resp="CBETA" type="mod">光明＝光光【宋】【元】【明】</note><app n="0509028"><lem wit="【大】">光明</lem><rdg resp="Taisho" wit="【宋】【元】【明】">光光</rdg></app>結<note n="0509029" resp="Taisho" place="foot text" type="orig">加＝跏【三】</note><note n="0509029" resp="CBETA" type="mod">加＝跏【宋】【元】【明】</note><app n="0509029"><lem wit="【大】">加</lem><rdg resp="Taisho" wit="【宋】【元】【明】">跏</rdg></app>趺坐。
<lb n="0509b20" ed="T"/>賢者指鬘翼從左右。還至祇樹給孤獨園。指
<lb n="0509b21" ed="T"/>鬘蒙化眾祐所信。諸<note n="0509030" resp="Taisho" place="foot text" type="orig">尊＝賢【三】</note><note n="0509030" resp="CBETA" type="mod">尊＝賢【宋】【元】【明】</note><app n="0509030"><lem wit="【大】">尊</lem><rdg resp="Taisho" wit="【宋】【元】【明】">賢</rdg></app>弟子亦共攝持。其族
<lb n="0509b22" ed="T"/>姓子。下鬚髮者<note n="0509031" resp="Taisho" place="foot text" type="orig">則＝即【三】</note><note n="0509031" resp="CBETA" type="mod">則＝即【宋】【元】【明】</note><app n="0509031"><lem wit="【大】">則</lem><rdg resp="Taisho" wit="【宋】【元】【明】">即</rdg></app><note n="0509032" resp="Taisho" place="foot text" type="orig">被＝披【宋】【元】</note><app n="0509032"><lem wit="【大】">被</lem><rdg resp="Taisho" wit="【宋】【元】">披</rdg></app>法服。以家之信捨家
<lb n="0509b23" ed="T"/>為道。具足究竟無上梵行。得六通證生死已
<lb n="0509b24" ed="T"/>斷。稱舉<note n="0509033" resp="Taisho" place="foot text" type="orig">淨＝清【三】</note><note n="0509033" resp="CBETA" type="mod">淨＝清【宋】【元】【明】</note><app n="0509033"><lem wit="【大】">淨</lem><rdg resp="Taisho" wit="【宋】【元】【明】">清</rdg></app>德所作已辦。解名色本即得應
<lb n="0509b25" ed="T"/>真。</p>
<lb n="0509b26" ed="T"/><p id="pT02p0509b2601">時王<note n="0509034" resp="Taisho" place="foot text" type="orig">波私匿＝波斯匿【三】</note><note n="0509034" resp="CBETA" type="mod">波私匿＝波斯匿【宋】【元】【明】</note><app n="0509034"><lem wit="【大】">波私匿</lem><rdg resp="Taisho" wit="【宋】【元】【明】">波斯匿</rdg></app><note n="0509035" resp="Taisho" place="foot text" type="orig">〔晉號和悅〕－【三】</note><note n="0509035" resp="CBETA" type="mod">〔晉號和悅〕－【宋】【元】【明】</note><app n="0509035"><lem wit="【大】"><note place="inline">晉號和悅</note></lem><rdg resp="Taisho" wit="【宋】【元】【明】">&lac;</rdg></app>。與四部眾象馬步騎。嚴駕
<lb n="0509b27" ed="T"/>出征欲討穢逆。<note n="0509036" resp="Taisho" place="foot text" type="orig">其＝王【三】</note><note n="0509036" resp="CBETA" type="mod">其＝王【宋】【元】【明】</note><app n="0509036"><lem wit="【大】">其</lem><rdg resp="Taisho" wit="【宋】【元】【明】">王</rdg></app>身疲弊而被塵土。過詣佛
<lb n="0509b28" ed="T"/>所稽首足下。佛問。王曰。從何所來身被塵土。
<lb n="0509b29" ed="T"/>王白佛言。唯然世尊。有大逆賊名<app source="0508007" type="＊"><lem wit="【大】">鴦掘摩</lem><rdg resp="Taisho" wit="【明】">鴦崛摩</rdg></app>。
<pb n="0509c" id="T02.0118.0509c" ed="T"/>
<lb n="0509c01" ed="T"/>兇暴懷害斷四徼道。手執嚴刃傷殺人民。今
<lb n="0509c02" ed="T"/>故<note n="0509037" resp="Taisho" place="foot text" type="orig">匡＝總【三】</note><note n="0509037" resp="CBETA" type="mod">匡＝總【宋】【元】【明】</note><app n="0509037"><lem wit="【大】">匡</lem><rdg resp="Taisho" wit="【宋】【元】【明】">總</rdg></app>勒四部之眾欲出討捕。是時指鬘在於
<lb n="0509c03" ed="T"/>會中。去佛不遠。佛告王曰。指鬘在此。已除鬚
<lb n="0509c04" ed="T"/>髮今為比丘。本<note n="0509038" resp="Taisho" place="foot text" type="orig">與＝舉【三】</note><note n="0509038" resp="CBETA" type="mod">與＝舉【宋】【元】【明】</note><app n="0509038"><lem wit="【大】">與</lem><rdg resp="Taisho" wit="【宋】【元】【明】">舉</rdg></app>云何。王白佛言。已志于
<lb n="0509c05" ed="T"/>道無如之何。當盡形壽給其衣食臥起床<note n="0509039" resp="Taisho" place="foot text" type="orig">坐＝座【明】</note><app n="0509039"><lem wit="【大】">坐</lem><rdg resp="Taisho" wit="【明】">座</rdg></app>
<lb n="0509c06" ed="T"/>病瘦醫藥。又問世尊。唯然大聖。<note n="0509040" resp="Taisho" place="foot text" type="orig">凶＝兇【元】【明】＊</note><app n="0509040"><lem wit="【大】">凶</lem><rdg resp="Taisho" wit="【元】【明】">兇</rdg></app>害逆人
<lb n="0509c07" ed="T"/>焉得至道履行寂義乎。今為安在。佛告王曰。
<lb n="0509c08" ed="T"/>近在斯坐。王遙見之。心即懷懼衣毛為&CB00594;。佛
<lb n="0509c09" ed="T"/>言。大王。莫恐莫懅。今以仁賢無復逆意。王
<lb n="0509c10" ed="T"/>造禮之謂曰。賢者。是指鬘乎。答曰。是也。
<lb n="0509c11" ed="T"/>王又問曰。仁姓為何。曰。奇角<note n="0509041" resp="Taisho" place="foot text" type="orig">氏＋（也）【三】</note><note n="0509041" resp="CBETA" type="mod">氏＋（也）【宋】【元】【明】</note><app n="0509041"><lem wit="【大】">氏</lem><rdg resp="Taisho" wit="【宋】【元】【明】">氏也</rdg></app>。又<note n="0509042" resp="Taisho" place="foot text" type="orig">問＋（曰）【三】</note><note n="0509042" resp="CBETA" type="mod">問＋（曰）【宋】【元】【明】</note><app n="0509042"><lem wit="【大】">問</lem><rdg resp="Taisho" wit="【宋】【元】【明】">問曰</rdg></app>。何
<lb n="0509c12" ed="T"/>謂奇角氏。曰父本姓。王曰。唯奇角子受吾供
<lb n="0509c13" ed="T"/>養。衣食床臥病瘦醫藥各盡形壽。即然所供。
<lb n="0509c14" ed="T"/>王<note n="0509043" resp="Taisho" place="foot text" type="orig">以＝唯【三】</note><note n="0509043" resp="CBETA" type="mod">以＝唯【宋】【元】【明】</note><app n="0509043"><lem wit="【大】">以</lem><rdg resp="Taisho" wit="【宋】【元】【明】">唯</rdg></app>獲許稽首辭還。歎世尊曰。能調諸不
<lb n="0509c15" ed="T"/>調。能成諸未成。安住垂大慈。無所不開<note n="0509044" resp="Taisho" place="foot text" type="orig">道＝導【三】</note><note n="0509044" resp="CBETA" type="mod">道＝導【宋】【元】【明】</note><app n="0509044"><lem wit="【大】">道</lem><rdg resp="Taisho" wit="【宋】【元】【明】">導</rdg></app>。
<lb n="0509c16" ed="T"/>消伏患逆使充法會。亦令&CB00848;庶逮斯調定。我
<lb n="0509c17" ed="T"/>國多事意欲請退。佛告。便去從<note n="0509045" resp="Taisho" place="foot text" type="orig">志＝心【三】</note><note n="0509045" resp="CBETA" type="mod">志＝心【宋】【元】【明】</note><app n="0509045"><lem wit="【大】">志</lem><rdg resp="Taisho" wit="【宋】【元】【明】">心</rdg></app>所奉。王
<lb n="0509c18" ed="T"/>禮佛足稽首而歸。</p>
<lb n="0509c19" ed="T"/><p id="pT02p0509c1901">爾時賢者指鬘。處於閑居服五納衣。明旦持
<lb n="0509c20" ed="T"/>&CB00425;入舍衛城普行分衛。見有諸家懷妊女人。
<lb n="0509c21" ed="T"/>月滿產難心歸怙之。問指鬘曰。欲何至趣唯
<lb n="0509c22" ed="T"/>蒙救濟。指鬘得供出城食畢。澡竟去器獨坐
<lb n="0509c23" ed="T"/>加敬。詣佛稽首白世尊曰。我朝晨旦著衣持
<lb n="0509c24" ed="T"/>&CB00425;入城分衛。見有女人臨月欲產。產難恐懼
<lb n="0509c25" ed="T"/>求見<note n="0509046" resp="Taisho" place="foot text" type="orig">救＝擁【三】</note><note n="0509046" resp="CBETA" type="mod">救＝擁【宋】【元】【明】</note><app n="0509046"><lem wit="【大】">救</lem><rdg resp="Taisho" wit="【宋】【元】【明】">擁</rdg></app>護。佛告指鬘。汝便速往謂女人曰。
<lb n="0509c26" ed="T"/>如指鬘言至誠不虛。從生<app source="0509020" type="＊"><lem wit="【大】">已</lem><rdg resp="Taisho" wit="【宋】【元】【明】">以</rdg></app>來未<note n="0509047" resp="Taisho" place="foot text" type="orig">嘗＝曾【三】</note><note n="0509047" resp="CBETA" type="mod">嘗＝曾【宋】【元】【明】</note><app n="0509047"><lem wit="【大】">嘗</lem><rdg resp="Taisho" wit="【宋】【元】【明】">曾</rdg></app>殺生。
<lb n="0509c27" ed="T"/>審如是者。姊當尋<note n="0509048" resp="Taisho" place="foot text" type="orig">生＝產【三】</note><note n="0509048" resp="CBETA" type="mod">生＝產【宋】【元】【明】</note><app n="0509048"><lem wit="【大】">生</lem><rdg resp="Taisho" wit="【宋】【元】【明】">產</rdg></app>安隱無患。指鬘白佛。
<lb n="0509c28" ed="T"/>我作眾罪不可稱計。發九十九人一不滿百。
<lb n="0509c29" ed="T"/>而發此言豈非兩舌乎。世尊告曰。前生異世
<pb n="0510a" id="T02.0118.0510a" ed="T"/>
<lb n="0510a01" ed="T"/>今生不同。是則至誠不為妄語。<note n="0510001" resp="Taisho" place="foot text" type="orig">如＝汝【三】</note><note n="0510001" resp="CBETA" type="mod">如＝汝【宋】【元】【明】</note><app n="0510001"><lem wit="【大】">如</lem><rdg resp="Taisho" wit="【宋】【元】【明】">汝</rdg></app>斯用時救
<lb n="0510a02" ed="T"/>彼女厄。即奉聖旨往到女<note n="0510002" resp="Taisho" place="foot text" type="orig">所＝許【宋】</note><app n="0510002"><lem wit="【大】">所</lem><rdg resp="Taisho" wit="【宋】">許</rdg></app>。如佛言曰。如
<lb n="0510a03" ed="T"/>我至誠所言不虛。從生<note n="0510003" resp="Taisho" place="foot text" type="orig">以＝已【宋】【元】</note><app n="0510003"><lem wit="【大】">以</lem><rdg resp="Taisho" wit="【宋】【元】">已</rdg></app>來未曾殺生。審
<lb n="0510a04" ed="T"/>如是者。當令大姊安隱在產。所言未竟女尋
<lb n="0510a05" ed="T"/><note n="0510004" resp="Taisho" place="foot text" type="orig">娩＝免【三】</note><note n="0510004" resp="CBETA" type="mod"><app><lem resp="CBETA.Maha">&CB01661;</lem><rdg wit="【大】">娩</rdg></app>＝免【宋】【元】【明】</note><app n="0510004"><lem wit="【大】">&CB01661;</lem><rdg resp="Taisho" wit="【宋】【元】【明】">免</rdg></app>軀兒亦獲安。</p>
<lb n="0510a06" ed="T"/><p id="pT02p0510a0601">爾時指鬘入舍衛城。群小童黻見之分衛。或
<lb n="0510a07" ed="T"/>瓦石擲或以箭射。或刀斫刺或杖捶擊。賢者
<lb n="0510a08" ed="T"/>指鬘。破頭傷體衣服<note n="0510005" resp="Taisho" place="foot text" type="orig">破裂＝破碎【三】</note><note n="0510005" resp="CBETA" type="mod">破裂＝破碎【宋】【元】【明】</note><app n="0510005"><lem wit="【大】">破裂</lem><rdg resp="Taisho" wit="【宋】【元】【明】">破碎</rdg></app><note n="0510006" resp="Taisho" place="foot text" type="orig">還＝甘【三】</note><note n="0510006" resp="CBETA" type="mod">還＝甘【宋】【元】【明】</note><app n="0510006"><lem wit="【大】">還</lem><rdg resp="Taisho" wit="【宋】【元】【明】">甘</rdg></app>詣佛所稽首
<lb n="0510a09" ed="T"/><note n="0510007" resp="Taisho" place="foot text" type="orig">足下起於佛前＝禮畢而歎【三】</note><note n="0510007" resp="CBETA" type="mod">足下起於佛前＝禮畢而歎【宋】【元】【明】</note><app n="0510007"><lem wit="【大】">足下起於佛前</lem><rdg resp="Taisho" wit="【宋】【元】【明】">禮畢而歎</rdg></app>頌曰。</p>
<lb n="0510a10" ed="T"/><lg id="lgT02p0510a1001"><l>我前本為賊</l><l>指鬘名普聞</l>
<lb n="0510a11" ed="T"/><l>大淵以枯竭</l><l>則歸命正覺</l>
<lb n="0510a12" ed="T"/><l>斯以<note n="0510008" resp="Taisho" place="foot text" type="orig">成＝戒【三】</note><note n="0510008" resp="CBETA" type="mod">成＝戒【宋】【元】【明】</note><app n="0510008"><lem wit="【大】">成</lem><rdg resp="Taisho" wit="【宋】【元】【明】">戒</rdg></app>忍辱</l><l>逮佛開化眾</l>
<lb n="0510a13" ed="T"/><l>聽經常以時</l><l>是故無躓礙</l>
<lb n="0510a14" ed="T"/><l>今<app source="0509020" type="＊"><lem wit="【大】">已</lem><rdg resp="Taisho" wit="【宋】【元】【明】">以</rdg></app>歸命佛</l><l>受真諦法戒</l>
<lb n="0510a15" ed="T"/><l>逮得三通達</l><l>則順諸佛教</l>
<lb n="0510a16" ed="T"/><l>昔暴懷兇毒</l><l>多傷眾類命</l>
<lb n="0510a17" ed="T"/><l>雖古多所危</l><l>吾今名無害</l>
<lb n="0510a18" ed="T"/><l>身口所犯過</l><l>志懷殺害心</l>
<lb n="0510a19" ed="T"/><l>其不危他餘</l><l>未曾遭諸厄</l>
<lb n="0510a20" ed="T"/><l>又復無過去</l><l><note n="0510009" resp="Taisho" place="foot text" type="orig">持其＝值母【三】</note><note n="0510009" resp="CBETA" type="mod">持其＝值母【宋】【元】【明】</note><app n="0510009"><lem wit="【大】">持其</lem><rdg resp="Taisho" wit="【宋】【元】【明】">值母</rdg></app>法寂然</l>
<lb n="0510a21" ed="T"/><l>應受<app source="0509040" type="＊"><lem wit="【大】">凶</lem><rdg resp="Taisho" wit="【元】【明】">兇</rdg></app>暴名</l><l>自調成仁賢</l>
<lb n="0510a22" ed="T"/><l>以才一調定</l><l>如鉤調諸象</l>
<lb n="0510a23" ed="T"/><l>如來成就我</l><l>無劍亦無杖</l>
<lb n="0510a24" ed="T"/><l>其前為放逸</l><l>然後能自制</l>
<lb n="0510a25" ed="T"/><l>彼明炤於世</l><l><note n="0510010" resp="Taisho" place="foot text" type="orig">由＝猶【三】＊</note><note n="0510010" resp="CBETA" type="mod">由＝猶【宋】＊【元】＊【明】＊</note><app n="0510010"><lem wit="【大】">由</lem><rdg resp="Taisho" wit="【宋】【元】【明】">猶</rdg></app>日出於雲</l>
<lb n="0510a26" ed="T"/><l>假使犯眾惡</l><l>不斷眾<note n="0510011" resp="Taisho" place="foot text" type="orig">善德＝菩提【三】</note><note n="0510011" resp="CBETA" type="mod">善德＝菩提【宋】【元】【明】</note><app n="0510011"><lem wit="【大】">善德</lem><rdg resp="Taisho" wit="【宋】【元】【明】">菩提</rdg></app></l>
<lb n="0510a27" ed="T"/><l>彼明炤於世</l><l><app source="0510010" type="＊"><lem wit="【大】">由</lem><rdg resp="Taisho" wit="【宋】【元】【明】">猶</rdg></app>雲消日出</l>
<lb n="0510a28" ed="T"/><l>若新學比丘</l><l>勤修於佛教</l>
<lb n="0510a29" ed="T"/><l>其明炤於世</l><l>如月盛滿時</l>
<pb n="0510b" id="T02.0118.0510b" ed="T"/>
<lb n="0510b01" ed="T"/><l>其有犯眾罪</l><l>當歸於<note n="0510012" resp="Taisho" place="foot text" type="orig">惡道＝惡趣【三】</note><note n="0510012" resp="CBETA" type="mod">惡道＝惡趣【宋】【元】【明】</note><app n="0510012"><lem wit="【大】">惡道</lem><rdg resp="Taisho" wit="【宋】【元】【明】">惡趣</rdg></app></l>
<lb n="0510b02" ed="T"/><l>不復難諸患</l><l><note n="0510013" resp="Taisho" place="foot text" type="orig">服＝飲【三】</note><note n="0510013" resp="CBETA" type="mod">服＝飲【宋】【元】【明】</note><app n="0510013"><lem wit="【大】">服</lem><rdg resp="Taisho" wit="【宋】【元】【明】">飲</rdg></app>食無所著</l>
<lb n="0510b03" ed="T"/><l>亦不求於生</l><l>未曾<note n="0510014" resp="Taisho" place="foot text" type="orig">會德＝貪惡【三】</note><note n="0510014" resp="CBETA" type="mod">會德＝貪惡【宋】【元】【明】</note><app n="0510014"><lem wit="【大】">會德</lem><rdg resp="Taisho" wit="【宋】【元】【明】">貪惡</rdg></app>死</l>
<lb n="0510b04" ed="T"/><l>唯須待時日</l><l>心常志於定</l>
<lb n="0510b05" ed="T"/><l>如是<app source="0508007" type="＊"><lem wit="【大】">鴦掘摩</lem><rdg resp="Taisho" wit="【明】">鴦崛摩</rdg></app></l><l>已得成羅漢</l>
<lb n="0510b06" ed="T"/><l>在佛世尊前</l><l>口自頌斯偈</l></lg>
<lb n="0510b07" ed="T"/><p id="pT02p0510b0701">佛說如是。賢者指鬘及諸比丘眾。聞經歡喜
<lb n="0510b08" ed="T"/><note n="0510015" resp="Taisho" place="foot text" type="orig">〔奉行〕－【三】</note><note n="0510015" resp="CBETA" type="mod">〔奉行〕－【宋】【元】【明】</note><app n="0510015"><lem wit="【大】">奉行</lem><rdg resp="Taisho" wit="【宋】【元】【明】">&lac;</rdg></app>。</p>
<lb n="0510b09" ed="T"/><juan n="001" fun="close"><jhead>佛說<app source="0508007" type="＊"><lem wit="【大】">鴦掘摩</lem><rdg resp="Taisho" wit="【明】">鴦崛摩</rdg></app>經</jhead></juan></div1>
</body></text></TEI.2>